name: Space-Exploration-Rocket-Part-Delivery
title: Space Exploration Rocket Part Delivery
author: I Ack Emma
description:
My own personal tweaks to the Space Exploration Pack
Adds the ability to send packed rocket components in delivery capsules to allow for easier cargo rocket based logistics, also increases the stack size of some items.
Credit to Earendel and the Space Exploration Mod for the icons in thumbnail
Visit: https://mods.factorio.com/mod/space-exploration
